From 6c074097419e41d09dc23308da000c5992bcbf18 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Wed, 24 Jun 2026 11:09:44 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Burn custom text into kham.mp4 via new ffmpeg backend
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Add a Bun+Hono backend service (Docker Compose) that burns the
user's custom text into kham.mp4 using ffmpeg drawtext, reusing the
styling/font from uimohamadrz/taghvimghafasi's main.py. The بساز
page now renders the actual video server-side and shares/downloads
the real mp4 instead of a DOM screenshot.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_01NeD1YgJ9J1SjRmubvFs6VG
